#: src/buildings.c:257
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the Larn Thrift Shoppe.`end`\n"
"\n"
"We stock many items explorers find useful in their adventures. Feel free to browse to your heart's content. Also be advised that if you break 'em, you pay for 'em."
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Willkommen im Gemischtwarenladen von Larn.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Wir fĂĽhren viele Waren, die Abenteurern auf ihren Reisen nĂĽtzlich sind. StĂ¶bere nach Herzenslust. Aber sei gewarnt: Wer etwas kaputt macht, bezahlt es auch."

#: src/buildings.c:342
msgid "Your home"
msgstr "Dein Zuhause"

#: src/buildings.c:344
#, c-format
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome home, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Latest word from the doctor is not good. The diagnosis is confirmed as dianthroritis. He guesses that your daughter has only %d mobuls left in this world. It's up to you, %s, to find the only hope for your daughter, the very rare potion of cure dianthroritis.  It is rumored that only deep in the depths of the caves can this potion be found.\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Willkommen zu Hause, %s.`end`\n"
"\n"
"Die letzten Nachrichten vom Doktor sind nicht gut. Die Diagnose lautet zweifelsfrei Dianthroritis. Er schĂ¤tzt, dass deiner Tochter nur noch %d Mobul auf dieser Welt bleiben. Es liegt an dir, %s, die einzige Hoffnung fĂĽr deine Tochter zu finden: den Ă¤uĂźerst seltenen Trank, der Dianthroritis heilt. Es heiĂźt, dieser Trank sei nur tief in den HĂ¶hlen zu finden.\n"

#: src/buildings.c:353
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Congratulations!`end` You found the potion of cure dianthroritis! Frankly, No one thought you could do it. Boy! Did you surprise them!\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`GlĂĽckwunsch!`end` Du hast den Trank gefunden, der Dianthroritis heilt! Ehrlich gesagt hat dir das niemand zugetraut. Junge, hast du sie ĂĽberrascht!\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:357
msgid ""
"The doctor has the sad duty to inform you that your daughter died before your return. There was nothing he could do without the potion.\n"
"\n"
"You didn't make it in time. Too bad..."
msgstr ""
"Der Doktor hat die traurige Pflicht, dir mitzuteilen, dass deine Tochter vor deiner RĂĽckkehr gestorben ist. Ohne den Trank konnte er nichts fĂĽr sie tun.\n"
"\n"
"Du hast es nicht rechtzeitig geschafft. Wie schade..."

#: src/buildings.c:362
msgid ""
"The doctor is now administering the potion and, in a few moments, your daughter should be well on her way to recovery.\n"
"\n"
"The potion is working! The doctor thinks that your daughter will recover in a few days.\n"
"\n"
"Congratulations!"
msgstr ""
"Der Doktor verabreicht nun den Trank, und in wenigen Augenblicken sollte sich deine Tochter auf dem Weg der Besserung befinden.\n"
"\n"
"Der Trank wirkt! Der Doktor glaubt, dass sich deine Tochter in wenigen Tagen erholen wird.\n"
"\n"
"Herzlichen GlĂĽckwunsch!"

#: src/buildings.c:380 src/player.c:1095
msgid "You saved your daughter!"
msgstr "Du hast deine Tochter gerettet!"

#: src/buildings.c:400 src/buildings.c:411
msgid "You were too late!"
msgstr "Du kamst zu spĂ¤t!"

