#: src/buildings.c:767
msgid ""
"`EMPH`Welcome to the College of Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"We offer the exciting opportunity of higher education to all inhabitants of the caves. Here is a list of the class schedule:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"`EMPH`Willkommen an der Hochschule von Larn!`end`\n"
"\n"
"Wir bieten allen Bewohnern der HĂ¶hlen die aufregende MĂ¶glichkeit hĂ¶herer Bildung. Hier ist der Stundenplan:\n"
"\n"

#: src/buildings.c:772
#, c-format
msgid "Sorry, but this class has a prerequisite of \"%s\"."
msgstr "Entschuldige, aber dieser Kurs setzt â€ž%sâ€ś voraus."

#: src/buildings.c:790
#, c-format
